item.title: A More Comprehensive Doomfist Guide

meta.summary:
b"Timestamps below if you want to skip to a particular section.

I made this guide to clear up misunderstandings with Doomfist and present a comprehensive and accurate guide in a clear, easy-to-understand manner. There are plenty of other Doomfist guides out there but they seem to all be either, for specific aspects of playing Doomfist, in confusing or inconvenient formats, feature misinformation or encourage bad habits. I don't claim to be the best Doomfist player out there but I'm certainly a good one!
